I guess I have a part in the death of SHWI, as life has caught up with
me and I've just been insanely busy lately, so I haven't had that much
time to post but a couple of thoughts on how to save SHWI;

Perhaps a SHWI collective blog?  A lot of people just don't know what
usenet is anymore, but perhaps a collective blog where we posted the
best of SHWI (with the author's permision of course) as well as new
material, could draw more people in and make someone who is interested
in AH aware that SHWI exists.

Membership drive?  Everyone try to get one new person who they know,
either on line or in real life, to give SHWI a shot.

I've suggested this before and some said it sounded good but no one
took me up on it; a buddy-system, ie I'll post a new Ishiwara Option
by the end of the month if you post a new FDR Dies, or whatever.

